<title>UK: Hall Engineering says to sell Stadco Auto.</title>
<headline>Hall Engineering says to sell Stadco Auto.</headline>
<dateline>1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Britain's Hall Engineering said on Tuesday that it had entered into agreement to dispose one of its divisions, Stadco Automation, to Estil for a total consideration of 8.4 million stg.</p>
<p>Stadco Automation was a division of Hall's subsidiary Stadco Ltd.</p>
